{"tid":1500492,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［不要文革化］應承我，幾嬲都好，繼續連結香港人","createTime":"2019-08-24T04:44:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T11:06:41.000Z","uid":79965,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"36e473978dc79de437774af223010a71b757d6da","tid":1500492,"uid":79965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T04:44:17.000Z","msg":"先講重點，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府以拉一派打一派分裂抗爭者，狀況仍然持續。最近以同樣招式對付各個群體：專業人士，家庭，社會大眾，務求令到每個人怕被篤灰，甚至想先下手為強對付異見者。我係呢到，懇求大家不要讓仇恨支配自己，人不犯我，我不犯人。唔好因為恐懼、憤怒，成為你唔想變成嘅人。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔知最近大家身邊係咪都多左呢幾班人，<br />\n<br />\n覺得抗爭無用，政府打壓越黎越勁，上一輩經歷過<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">六四</span></span>嘅人，開始叫後生仔少D出去。常見對白係：「就算係有問題，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁又點姐？你可以做到D咩呀？</span></span>」聽到<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">悲觀主義者</span></span>嘅對白唔好嬲，因為成大事者，往往要<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Think like a pessimist, and act like an optimist</span></span>. <br />\n<br />\n覺得阻人搵食，甚至唔係阻自己，而係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">其他人俾你阻到搵食好慘呀</span></strong></span>嘅人。常見對白係：「<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你班後生都無挨過窮，試過食樹皮你就唔會搞搞震啦！</span></span>」聽到務實主義者嘅對白唔好嬲，因為你同我都<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">應該要理解其他人嘅痛苦</span></span>。對於我地黎講，失去自由係痛苦嘅；對於佢地黎講，活係飢餓、貧窮下係痛苦嘅。佢地從來無嘗試了解我地，但我地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">必須要了解他人，才能連結群眾</span></span>。佢地都唔會反對追求自由、正義係有問題，佢地擔心嘅係佢哋嘅<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其他concern</span></span>不被保障。最緊要記得，呢個世界無絕對嘅啱同錯。對住呢班人最緊要記得自己嘅遠景，相信自己，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">做自己認為正確嘅事</span></span>，就可以了。<br />\n<br />\n極端主義者，覺得抗爭者<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔抵可憐，應該要死</span></span>。呢一班人，放諸任何社會都係最有問題<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最恐怖嘅人</span></span>，情況就好似恐怖份子咁。可憐之人必有可恨之處，反之亦然。我係呢到懇求大家，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不要被仇恨支配自己</span></span>。佢斬人你輯兇可以，但唔好因為仇恨而做更多嘅事，唔好變成<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">濫用私刑嘅黑警</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n我地嘅同路人好多，但唔係一句我地係同路人，就每個人都可以接受你做嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所有事情</span></span>。每個人<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">底線不一</span></span>，所以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好期望所有人認同你所有事</span></span>。重點係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">做嘢嘅時候盡量令同路人明白，係我地每一個人嘅責任。不分化，不割蓆。未來幾個星期係最關鍵嘅時候。「我地」千萬唔好散！</span></span>"},{"pid":"a5d8f4f843aeeb24f68854a5d1a4f051f2e96f6d","tid":1500492,"uid":175159,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T04:47:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cxZ0eYC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcxZ0eYC.jpg&h=f5feb5a5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EQJTzYC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEQJTzYC.jpg&h=ce0315f5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8EfiL5i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8EfiL5i.jpg&h=aee17494&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ptpocLi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FptpocLi.png&h=92b50e6b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z2NEvwY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz2NEvwY.jpg&h=5172e70f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f42cfa498e45a4c09c70b543303f99b8ca28668d","tid":1500492,"uid":256296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T04:47:34.000Z","msg":"香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3946c8c8aae31d52fe6705cc9ceb81ebfff9a3ca","ti